    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是 Puyo Puyo 的粉丝还是拼图街机的粉丝？让自己沉浸在五彩缤纷的梅奥梅奥世界中，灵感来自快餐、酱汁和调味品。在这款 Match-4 拼图中玩蓝色、芥末酱、蛋黄酱、芥末酱和番茄酱，这将考验你的反应能力和聪明才智。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试玩版提供了不同模式的体验：包含 20 个关卡的第一个益智模式世界、5 分钟的生存模式（简单难度）以及与简单 AI 进行的多人比赛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/e72a41a00556fd6d955f8faa3332f00c.poster.avif?t=1731057027\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/e72a41a00556fd6d955f8faa3332f00c.webm?t=1731057027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/e72a41a00556fd6d955f8faa3332f00c.mp4?t=1731057027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用拼图模式，获得壮观的连击。通过 160 个渐进难度级别来提高你的思维和反应能力</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/02f58b4c011cd3c55884e2d9665e186e.poster.avif?t=1731057027\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/02f58b4c011cd3c55884e2d9665e186e.webm?t=1731057027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/02f58b4c011cd3c55884e2d9665e186e.mp4?t=1731057027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与来自世界各地的玩家或朋友一起沉浸在在线或本地多人游戏中。为最多 4 名玩家创建公共或私人游戏。你也可以面对所有级别的人工智能来进步，但要小心，它们不会给你带来任何好处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/05ad66ec00f9219dbd24e459333e5286.poster.avif?t=1731057027\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/05ad66ec00f9219dbd24e459333e5286.webm?t=1731057027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/05ad66ec00f9219dbd24e459333e5286.mp4?t=1731057027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对唱片充满热情？生存模式及其3个难度级别为您提供无尽的体验，挑战您并突破极限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/c9183e2e3ae2487f75911df33e3a326c.poster.avif?t=1731057027\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/c9183e2e3ae2487f75911df33e3a326c.webm?t=1731057027\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271510/extras/c9183e2e3ae2487f75911df33e3a326c.mp4?t=1731057027\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >训练模式允许你激活各种设置来帮助你提高技能。花点时间来探索这个易于学习但很难掌握的游戏！</p>",
